				\begin{document}$${\chi }_{R}^{2}$$\end{document}χR2 = 2.351). In the case of QD655 encapsulated into DOPC:DOPS-liposomes, the intensity-weighted average decay time of the triexponential fit analysis increased to τav(int) = 41.4 ± 2.09 ns (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
